These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, cola
There 2 different types of food: onion, cabbage
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | cola  | water |
| Food       | onion | cabbage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | milk | sprite |
| Sport      | cricket     | skiing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, horror
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, turkish
1. the indian is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
2. the indian is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | horror  |
| Nationality   | indian | turkish |

 #################################

 
