.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: argentine, canadian
2 different pets are kept: ferret, horse
1. the canadian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
2. the owner of the horse is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | argentine | canadian |
| Pet           | horse     | ferret  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: collecting, video-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, librarian
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | video-games | collecting |
| Job     | project-manager        | librarian |

